      "text": "OmegaFlow is a Python CLI for rebuildable terminal videos with generated voiceover. It can record any terminal workflow. Start in your project's Python environment. If you do not have one yet, create one first. Then install OmegaFlow. The omegaflow command is ready for the rest of the workflow.",
